Information taken from , personal understanding, and online  sources Wikipedia.
"


**To every student reading this — your worth isn’t in how pretty your borders look, it’s in the effort, clarity, and knowledge you bring to the table. And to CBSE — if ASL is truly about speaking and listening, then judge us on our voice and our words, not our glitter pens. Education should measure minds, not margins.**

